Direct Known Subclasses:
CrossoverOperatorSelecterImpl, MutateOperatorSelecterImpl, NEATCrossoverOperatorSelecterImpl, NEATMutateOperatorSelecterImpl
public abstract class AbstractOperatorSelecter<O extends Operator<?>>
extends AbstractEvolutionObject
implements OperatorSelecter<O>

AbstractOperatorSelecter implements the OperatorSelecter interface. It uses roulette selection to choose an operator. Selected operators are made unavailable for selection again until the reset method is called.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
